Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说还真棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟有不少老油子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压制边境可不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有些地方没压制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这样子 马上又要轮到我们上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博格队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完毕立刻出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个目标定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算换班了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 天气真的转冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么 不是冷的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你珍藏的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那是酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被队长发现会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在执行任务 交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真有那种混蛋老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神出奇好 专门找差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我之前的队长 光摆着一副架子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别有距高感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种队伍 还不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫时待命 移动目标可能有变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时是等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看作战会议上怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今天之内是定不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 这么冷的天要野管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 期间会维护神通的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有指令了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我们几个?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机修组会依次过来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预定时间是23点整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 没空睡觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,21点整之前自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡觉喝酒都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到点前恢复清醒就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 挺···
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐的口味好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家一直夸莉莉品味独特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算不上夸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 我要告诉你爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤儿院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道该不该这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有一对老夫妇收留了战争中的孤儿们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 希望送点礼物给孤儿院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉之前说错话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说错话?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没注意说了句「要告诉他爸妈」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以过去吗 虽然那里有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到点之前回来就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小礼物 以表心意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前还是敌人 可能不太好收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们收下了 你们客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你们两个人照顾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始没打算照顾他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:06:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他们自己聚过来了 又不能放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在更像是他们在照顾我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能一直这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大家画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 阿妮娅和大家画的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨的时候 他们画着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这幅画···
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个孩子画的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算叫她画点别的 还是只画战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种世界成了她现在的日常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前不久我们还在攻击这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再凑近点看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出奥秘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是行家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起画画吧 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 不能呆太久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再留一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回去 记得留时间睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要通青维护了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了 你们猜猜是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你画了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想画这里的老爷爷和老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是别告诉他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然小孩无法理解莉莉的审美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请要要点心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到艾玛的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫艾玛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是你家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望那里永远都是孩子们的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是假设
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你现在觉得自己无处可归
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后一定会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前对遇见的孩子这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时这么说是想安慰她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也一直在寻找归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把我养大的家里 也没有归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方我们很难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了生存才流落到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没把军队当自己的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 莉莉也觉得军队不是自己的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这支分队 大家在的地方就像归宿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才盖尔队长说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「记得留时间睡觉 要通宵维护了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像呼嗦的爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看布雷克兵曹长和盖伊那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时还挺温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然休伊是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总会有那么一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每家都有个头疼的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我以前就想要个帅气的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果斯黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也把这个分队当归宿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想拿这种表情糊弄过去 没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道该怎么回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手别停听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经决定下一个移动地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里往南120公里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在利奧·塔克拉斯州边上和强袭空母汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压制或破坏王国军设施
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来一个烫手山芋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6点30分出 发维护在两小时内结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你也把这个分队当归宿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到艾玛的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是只会笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前也是这种孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样笑着就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样什么事都能忍过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续 继续 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往右一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机修组已经走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会有办法的 大家先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计花一两个小时 我会追上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 你来帮忙 斯黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见 居然会犯这种错误
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 偶尔发现你像人的一面也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种意义上 战场是最看得清人本性的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是硬派强壮的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了前线也会因恐惧吓得胆怯 哭喊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想像你一样保持平常心 都装不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有装
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为你抛弃了感情活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得自己变了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道这样子像不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后还能呆在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕很难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光靠这对老夫妇太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的地方还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们能力有限
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总比什么都不做好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才开了孤儿院?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见那幅画了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的孤儿院里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会画战争血腥场景的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把孩子弄成那样的人就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们有责任看到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让孩子们看到不同的世界 不同的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 好好开车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是又发呆撞上了 我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长像个啰嗦的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧 我受够孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就到利奥·塔克拉斯州了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能走了 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲在掩体里打我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别退缩 应战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毁机枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走那边 走那块斜坡上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是地雷 斜坡上埋了地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后退 别离开线路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 是想彻底挡住我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架势是坚决不让我们接近设施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那设施里到底有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能撤回去 舰炮射击要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会摧毁雷区的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 盖伊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好···
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是悬浮器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆一边喝酒去吧 剩下的交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了盖伊 那家伙关键时刻掉链子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉 身后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台机体···
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后退 要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护重要的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休伊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖伊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后替我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争结束 之后的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 安睡在我们面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索莱伊王国军身经百战的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德·米勒骑士团总长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国皇帝开恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顾敌我关系 向您的死致以由衷的哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且静静收起汝向吾等亮出的利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛把敌人的葬礼办得这么隆重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是某种宣传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣传？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟迟不完的战争 对方也一样累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要煽动对方的厌战情绪 瓦解他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有的人战死连具尸体都没留
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然队长不挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但唯独不吃这个豆子料理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在执行任务 交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:14.05,标题,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1628,910)}{\fad(1000,1000)}灵魂的发火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,99)}你好 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}现在安详地驾鹤归西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}若非天时与立场将我们阻隔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}怕是不会白刃相向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}而是举杯共酌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,97)}畅谈各自效忠国家的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:40.08,标题2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,102)}二人的决心
